---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Teaching" description="Courses I've taught or assisted in, across social science and data science">
  <div class="space-y-12">
    <header>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-2">Teaching</h1>
      <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Courses I've taught or assisted in, across social science and data science</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">Short Courses</h2>

      <div class="divide-y divide-border dark:divide-border-dark">
        <div class="py-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Agentes de IA para pesquisa em ciências sociais: uma introdução ao Claude Code</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark"><a href="https://ceres-iesp.uerj.br" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CERES</a>, IESP-UERJ · May 2026</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="py-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Machine Learning</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">Methodological Training of <a href="https://mape.org.br/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MAPE</a> · 2025.2 · Graduate</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
              <a href="https://github.com/felipelmc/Presentations/tree/main/ML-FMMAPE-2025" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Files →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Fundamentals of machine learning, focusing on recognizing, training, interpreting, and evaluating simple predictive models applied to social research.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Deep Learning & Text-as-Data</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">10th Student Week of the Postgraduate Programs, IESP-UERJ · 2025.2 · Graduate</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
              <a href="https://github.com/felipelmc/Presentations/tree/main/Minicurso-DL-Jornada-Discente-IESP-2025" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Files →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Fundamentals of deep learning: what it is and how to train a neural network, and text-as-data with deep learning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">Teaching Assistance</h2>

      <div class="divide-y divide-border dark:divide-border-dark">
        <div class="py-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Advanced Text-as-Data</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">IESP-UERJ Winter School · 2025.1 · Graduate</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
              <a href="https://tiagoventura.github.io/tad_iesp_workshop/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Course website →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Deep Learning, Transformers, Embeddings, and Large Language Models applied to political science research. Instructors: <a href="https://www.venturatiago.com/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tiago Ventura</a>, Ph.D., and <a href="https://www.svallejovera.com/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sebastián Vallejo Vera</a>, Ph.D.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Quantitative Methods II</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">FGV CPDOC · 2024.2 · Undergraduate</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Exploratory data analysis, basic statistical inference, and regression models. Instructor: <a href="https://cpdoc.fgv.br/equipe/jaironicolau" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jairo Nicolau</a>, Ph.D.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Introduction to R</span>
              <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">FGV CPDOC · 2020.2 · Graduate</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Introduction to programming for social sciences. Instructor: <a href="https://cpdoc.fgv.br/equipe/JimmyMedeiros" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jimmy Medeiros</a>, Ph.D.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
